text: Herbert Wetter (15 March 1891 - 5 September 1966) was a Norwegian swimmer. He competed in the men's 1500 metre freestyle event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. He represented the club Oslo IL. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Norwegian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Norway Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nedre Eiker
